{"tid":2128733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【立法會選舉●區一】8有意參選民主派 表明願設退選機制","createTime":"2020-07-28T06:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T06:58:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9e6336eb5d4c3796a5216c14330cae5de2a330","tid":2128733,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/XEKM456IXZE7WO56B4QI3APOPM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FXEKM456IXZE7WO56B4QI3APOPM%2F&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=f41a388a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FXEKM456IXZE7WO56B4QI3APOPM%2F&h=a14755c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/XEKM456IXZE7WO56B4QI3APOPM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【立法會選舉●區一】8有意參選民主派 表明願設退選機制<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8jEHytBZTjdpRn86rSU3uQGkaUc=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RIH6FNV4T45CPRQ7QBLKXFWKG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8jEHytBZTjdpRn86rSU3uQGkaUc%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRIH6FNV4T45CPRQ7QBLKXFWKG4.jpg&h=451ba1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左起：李家偉、仇栩欣、陳振哲及麥德正<br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n去年民主派於區議會選舉大勝，新一屆立法會選舉區議會（第一）功能組別議席被視為民主派的囊中物，共有8人有意或已報名參選，並於昨晚（27日）出席民主派區議員舉辦的選舉論壇。昨日報名參選的民建聯劉珮玉亦有獲邀但未有出席，會上各名候選人都表明，願意建立機制，日後決定是否需要退選等以集中票源，避免建制派漁人得利。<br />\n<br />\n民主派區議員為有意循區一出選人士舉辦論壇，參與者除日前搶先報名的「機楊大叔」、大埔區議員陳振哲及荃灣區議員劉卓裕外，還有屯門區議員李家偉、新同盟大埔區議員任啟邦、東區區議員仇栩欣和工黨麥德正、南區區議員司馬文及黃大仙區議員莫灝哲。論壇除各人自我介紹及總結外，也分括主持個別提問、集體提問及自由問答環節。<br />\n<br />\n民主派初選抗。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他多次強調參選。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李家偉被質詢如何團結民主派<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【立法會選舉】建制大合奏施壓 政府料日內公佈押後選舉<br />\n<br />\n不少參與者都在自由答問。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n論壇上也觸及成功當選會。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n司馬文則多番強調區。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不少人倡議推動全民議政，如陳振哲。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"11d5cb6cae5611e702ccbba4f1aed82ebba0a572","tid":2128733,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}